Class KeyboardListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • Heroes_Villains.Listener.KeyboardListener

    public class KeyboardListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.KeyListener
    Listens for keyboard inputs and updates the appropriate variables. Implements KEyListener.
